OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,8,Fhas stepped up demands for Westminster
OL,9,Fto provide emergency support during
OL,10,Fthe cost of living crisis ` warning
OL,11,Fthat without action the UK is heading
OL,12,Ftowards a "cliff edge".
OL,14,FThe MP made the plea in the wake of
OL,15,Fwarnings from the Bank of England over
OL,16,Fthe state of the UK economy.
OL,26,@tD@KOUtD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FWhile stressing that the "severity and
OL,8,Fduration" of the current conflict in
OL,9,Fthe Gulf is unknown, the worst case
OL,10,Fscenario could see inflation peak at
OL,11,F6.2% and not drop back to the target
OL,12,Frate of 2% in the next four years.
OL,14,FSuch a scenario could see as many as
OL,15,Fsix interest rate rises to 5.5%, it
OL,16,Fwas reported.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FWarning that the UK is facing
OL,8,F"economic catastrophe", Mr Flynn
OL,9,Faccused Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,10,FStarmer of being "asleep at the wheel"
OL,11,Fwhen the Government should be
OL,12,Fproviding "urgent help".
OL,14,FHitting out at the Labour leader, the
OL,15,FMr Flynn ` who is hoping to be elected
OL,16,Fto Holyrood in next week's Scottish
OL,17,FParliament election ` said: "Broken
OL,18,FBrexit Britain is at crisis point and
OL,19,Fit's a disgrace that Keir Starmer is
OL,20,Fasleep at the wheel as the UK rapidly
OL,21,Fheads to a cliff edge."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@VO]rD@ROUrD@fO]tD@KOUtD@WO]yD@
OL,26,A]OU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FMr Flynn said: "The SNP has been
OL,8,Fwarning the Labour Party Government
OL,9,Ffor months that families, farmers and
OL,10,Fbusinesses need urgent help as the
OL,11,Fcost of living soars on Keir Starmer's
OL,12,Fwatch.
OL,14,F"The UK is facing an economic
OL,15,Fcatastrophe but the Labour Government
OL,16,Fhas done nothing, has no idea how to
OL,17,Ffix the mess and is completely
OL,18,Funprepared for the devastation that is
OL,19,Fcoming.
OL,26,@oD@POUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,F"While the UK faces yet another cost
OL,8,Fof living emergency, sleepy Starmer is
OL,9,Fsitting on his hands while Scottish
OL,10,Ffamilies and businesses are battered
OL,11,Fby sky-high costs."
OL,13,FHe spoke out in the wake of Thursday's
OL,14,FBank of England Monetary Policy
OL,15,FCommittee meeting ` where interest
OL,16,Frates were held steady at 3.75% but
OL,17,Fmembers stressed they were alert to
OL,18,Fthe evolving situation in the Middle
OL,19,FEast.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FMr Flynn said warnings of the impact
OL,8,Fthe conflict could have on possible
OL,9,Fincreases in inflation and interest
OL,10,Frates were "devastating and could
OL,11,Fcripple hard-pressed families with
OL,12,Frising mortgage rates, food prices and
OL,13,Ffuel prices that are completely
OL,14,Funaffordable".
OL,16,FThis, he warned, would be the scenario
OL,17,F"unless the UK Government wakes up and
OL,18,Ftakes action now".
OL,26,@rD@LOUvD@MO]yD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FMr Flynn demanded: "It is essential
OL,8,Fthat the UK Government follows the
OL,9,Fexample of independent countries like
OL,10,FIreland and delivers an emergency
OL,11,Fpackage of financial support.
OL,13,F"That must include removing VAT from
OL,14,Ffuel for the duration of the crisis,
OL,15,Fscrapping its planned hike to fuel
OL,16,Fduty, and introducing a Household
OL,17,FEnergy Price Cap to lower bills by
OL,18,Fhundreds of pounds."
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,FThe SNP MP sought to contrast the
OL,8,Factions of ministers in England with
OL,9,Fpoliticians in Scotland, claiming that
OL,10,Fwhile "John Swinney's SNP Government
OL,11,Fis laser-focused on delivering the
OL,12,Fstrongest cost of living support for
OL,13,Ffamilies anywhere in the UK, the
OL,14,FLabour Government has no plan at all".
OL,16,FMeanwhile Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,17,Fsaid: "The war in the Middle East is
OL,18,Fnot our war, but it is one we have to
OL,19,Frespond to.
OL,26,@rD@GOUvD@eO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,F"Every choice I make will be about
OL,8,Fkeeping costs down for families and
OL,9,Fbusinesses, without repeating the
OL,10,Fmistakes we've seen in the past that
OL,11,Fresulted in higher inflation and
OL,12,Fhigher interest rates.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777619131
OL,3,CStephen Flynn calls for emergency
OL,4,Cfinancial support as UK faces 'cliff
OL,5,Cedge'
OL,7,F"We entered this conflict in a
OL,8,Fstronger position because of the
OL,9,Fchoices this Government took to build
OL,10,Feconomic stability, and we are going
OL,11,Ffurther to take back our energy
OL,12,Fsecurity, backing British industry and
OL,13,Fprotecting households, to build a
OL,14,FBritain that is stronger, more
OL,15,Fresilient, and prepared for the
OL,16,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
